course_title: Assessment and Treatment Planning for Advanced Periodontal Diseases

sections.comments: This is a "Wait List" for Section 99C of DHYG 433 offered in January.

This section of the course is ONLINE- distance education. Your instructor and course support staff will contact you by email prior to and during the course. Please ensure you have a valid email account through.  You will need your Campus Wide Login (CWL) to login to your course at https://www.elearning.ubc.ca/ . Course materials must be ordered or picked up at the UBC Bookstore. More information can be found under Distance Learning at : http://ctlt.ubc.ca/ Admission to the Faculty of Dentistry is mandatory before registering (see website www.dentistry.ubc.ca)

description: Available in online distance education format only.
